            "type": "prose",
            "fields": {
                "heading": "Dependable cover through the night",
                "body": "Nights bring their own demands. Residents may need help settling, regular checks, and calm reassurance in the small hours, and a service is often running on a smaller team. Vigil Care Staffing supplies vetted night-shift care workers to care providers across Greater London. Our night workers are experienced in the rhythm of overnight care, quiet, attentive, and ready to respond when needed. We supply healthcare assistants, support workers, and specialist night staff for care homes, supported living, and private residences. From covering a single night to filling a longer run of shifts, we match reliable workers to your rota so overnight care stays safe and consistent.",
                "image": {
                    "id": 105,
                    "url": "https://res.cloudinary.com/duhicmygg/image/upload/v1782894931/vigil/care_staffing/general/night-shift-care-staff-london-assistance-care-staffing-london.webp",
