            "provenance": "later_editorial"
        },
        {
            "type": "text_image",
            "fields": {
                "heading": "Vetting and compliance for overnight placements",
                "body": "Overnight shifts often run with fewer people on site, so the workers we supply must be dependable and properly checked. Before any night placement, we complete enhanced DBS checks, verify right to work, and take up professional references. We assess relevant skills for the role, and because our workers are directly employed we keep training and documentation current. Our recruitment follows a CQC-compliant process, so night cover meets the same standard as any daytime placement.",
                "image": {
